## 5. Code and Technical Content

### Code Blocks

```python
def hello(name):
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")
```

### Terminal Output

& $ python script.py
& Hello, World!
& Process completed.

### Mathematical Formulas

Inline math: The value of π is approximately 3.14159.

Block math:

$$
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-x^2} dx = \sqrt{\pi}
$$

