## 7. Data and Calculations

### Variables and Math

$price = 99.99
$quantity = 3
$tax_rate = 0.08

**Subtotal:** ${{$price * $quantity}}
**Tax:** ${{$price * $quantity * $tax_rate}}
**Total:** ${{$price * $quantity * (1 + $tax_rate)}}

### Statistics

$scores = [85, 92, 78, 95, 88]

**Average:** {{ Math.round(List.avg($scores)) }}
**Highest:** {{ List.max($scores) }}
**Lowest:** {{ List.min($scores) }}

---

## 8. Dynamic Content with Loops

### Product List

$products = [
  {name: "Laptop", price: 999, in_stock: true},
  {name: "Mouse", price: 29, in_stock: true},
  {name: "Keyboard", price: 79, in_stock: false}
]

### Available Products

:::foreach {$products as $product}
:::if {$product.in_stock}
- **{$product.name}** - ${{$product.price}}
:::
:::
:::

### Team Members

$team = [
  {name: "Alice", role: "Developer", level: "Senior"},
  {name: "Bob", role: "Designer", level: "Junior"},
  {name: "Charlie", role: "Manager", level: "Senior"}
]

### Team Roster

:::foreach {$team as $member}
:::if {$member.level == "Senior"}
### 👤 {$member.name} — {$member.role} {.senior-badge}
:::
:::if {$member.level == "Junior"}
### 👤 {$member.name} — {$member.role}
:::
:::
:::

