## 10. Advanced Features

### Footnotes

Zolt supports footnotes for additional information[^1] and references[^note2].

You can reference the same footnote multiple times[^1].

[^1]: This is the first explanatory footnote.
[^note2]: This is the second footnote with more details.

### Abbreviations

Use abbreviations with tooltips:

HTML{abbr="HyperText Markup Language"} is the foundation of the web.
CSS{abbr="Cascading Style Sheets"} styles the HTML.
JS{abbr="JavaScript"} adds interactivity.

Global definitions:

*[API]: Application Programming Interface
*[URL]: Uniform Resource Locator

The API provides endpoints at various URLs.

### Dates

**Created:** {$created}
**Last Modified:** {$modified}

