## Appendix

### Keyboard Shortcuts

Common Zolt editor shortcuts:

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Ctrl+S` | Save document |
| `Ctrl+B` | Bold text |
| `Ctrl+I` | Italic text |
| `Ctrl+K` | Insert link |

### Troubleshooting

:::details [Common Issues]
**Issue:** Chart not displaying
**Solution:** Check data format and syntax

**Issue:** Loop not working
**Solution:** Verify array structure and variable names
:::

